Spacious and bright four-bedroom detached house in a great location, situated on the desirable west side of Louth within easy walking distance from the town centre. 

The house is surrounded on three sides by attractive mature gardens, with a single garage and further driveway parking for two cars. The rear garden features a good sized lawn, a secluded patio area which receives the sun for most of the day and a mature apple tree which provides shade and a bountiful supply of apples from late summer onwards. 

